overview.en: Redefining the underlying basic technology of the block chain and integrating the national and global data to form an effective link to provide a complete closed loop commercial leisure and entertainment platform for the users and businesses to achieve a win-win situation.
overview.zh: 利用区块链底层基础技术重新定义，整合全国乃至全球数据，形成有效链接为用户及商户之间提供完整的闭环商业休闲娱乐于一体的多元化平台建设，使之共赢
